\v 2 Ngiyalibabaza-ke\x + 11.17,22.\x*, bazalwane, ukuthi liyangikhumbula ezintweni zonke\x + 4.17.\x*, lokuthi libambelele ezimisweni\x + 15.2. 7.17. 1 Thes. 4.1,2.\x*\f + \fk izimiso: \fl kumbe, \fq imikhuba.\f* njengoba ngalinika.
\v 3 Kodwa ngithanda ukuthi lazi, ukuthi inhloko yawo wonke amadoda nguKristu\x + Efe. 5.23. Efe. 1.22; 4.15. Kol. 1.18.\x*; lenhloko yowesifazana yindoda\x + Gen. 3.16.\x*; lenhloko kaKristu nguNkulunkulu\x + 3.23; 15.27,28. Fil. 2.7,9. Joha. 14.28.\x*.
\v 4 Yonke indoda ekhulekayo loba eprofethayo\x + 12.10,28; 14.3,6,22,24,31,39. 1 Thes. 5.20. Seb. 19.6.\x*, ikhanda limboziwe, ilithela ihlazo ikhanda layo.
\v 5 Kodwa wonke owesifazana okhuleka kumbe aprofethe\x + 14.34. Luka 2.36. Seb. 21.9.\x* ikhanda lingambombozwanga, ulithela ihlazo\x + Nani 5.18.\x* elakhe ikhanda; ngoba lokhu kufanana-ke lophuciweyo\x + Dute. 21.12.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba uba owesifazana engagubuzeli, futhi kagele; kodwa uba kukubi\x + Micah 1.16.\x* kowesifazana ukugela kumbe ukuphucwa, kagutshuzelwe.
\v 7 Ngoba indoda kayifanele ukumbomboza ikhanda, ngoba ingumfanekiso\x + Gen. 1.26.\x* lodumo lukaNkulunkulu\x + 2 Kor. 3.7.\x*; kodwa owesifazana\x + Zaga 12.4.\x* uludumo lwendoda\x + 2 Kor. 3.7.\x*.
