\v 11 Kodwa indoda\x + Gal. 3.28.\x* kayingaphandle kowesifazana, lowesifazana kangaphandle kwendoda, eNkosini\x + 7.39.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba njengoba owesifazana\x + Gen. 2.21,23.\x* evela endodeni, ngokunjalo lendoda ivela ngowesifazana, kodwa konke kuvela kuNkulunkulu\x + 8.6.\x*.
\v 13 Ziboneleni lina\x + Luka 12.57. Joha. 7.24.\x*; kufanele yini ukuthi owesifazana akhuleke kuNkulunkulu engambombozanga?
\v 14 Imvelo uqobo lwayo kayilifundisi yini, ukuthi uba indoda ilenwele ezinde, kulihlazo kuyo?
\v 15 Kodwa uba owesifazana elenwele ezinde, kuludumo kuye. Ngoba inwele uziphiwe ukuthi zibe yisimbombozo.
\v 16 Kodwa uba umuntu\x + 1 Tim. 6.4.\x* ebonakala elenkani\x + 14.37. Mark. 10.42.\x*, thina kasilawo umkhuba onjalo, ngitsho lamabandla kaNkulunkulu\x + 4.17; 7.17; 14.33 & 16.1. 11.22. 11.32. Gal. 1.22. 1 Thes. 2.14.\x*.
