\v 17 Kodwa ngokulaya lokhu kangi\add li\add*babazi, ngoba libuthana ngokungekuhle kodwa ngokubi.
\v 18 Okokuqala ngoba nxa libuthana ebandleni, ngizwa ukuthi kukhona ukwehlukana phakathi kwenu\x + 3.3.\x*; njalo nganxanye ngiyakukholwa.
\v 19 Ngoba kufanele\x + Mat. 18.7. Luka 17.1. Seb. 20.30. 1 Tim. 4.1,2. 2 Pet. 2.1,2.\x* ukuba lobubhazuka\x + Gal. 5.20. 2 Pet. 2.1.\x* futhi phakathi kwenu, ukuze labo\x + Luka 2.35. 1 Joha. 2.19. Dute. 13.3. Zaga 28.12.\x* abaqinisileyo babonakale\x + 2 Kor. 13.7.\x* phakathi kwenu.
\v 20 Ngakho nxa libuthana ndawonye, \add lokhu\add* kakusikho ukudla isidlo seNkosi\x + Isam. 1.10.\x*;
\v 21 ngoba ngulowo lalowo uthatha kuqala esakhe isidlo ekudleni\x + Gen. 2.18.\x*, lomunye ulambile, lomunye udakiwe\x + 2 Pet. 2.13. Juda 1.12.\x*.
\v 22 Kanti kalilazo izindlu zokudlela lezokunathela? Kumbe lidelela ibandla likaNkulunkulu\x + 10.32.\x*, liyangise\x + Zaga 17.5. Jak. 2.6.\x* yini abangelakho? Ngingathini kini? Ngingalibabaza kulokhu yini? Kangi\add li\add*babazi.
