\v 23 Ngoba mina ngakwemukela\x + 15.3. Gal. 1.12. Seb. 22.14.\x* eNkosini, lokho lami engalinika khona, ukuthi iNkosi uJesu\x + 10.16; 14.16.11.25. Mat. 26.26,28. Mark. 14.22,24. Luka 22.19,20.\x* ngobusuku eyanikelwa ngabo yathatha isinkwa,
\v 24 isibongile ya\add si\add*hlephuna\x + Seb. 20.7.\x*, yathi: Thathani, lidle, lokhu kungumzimba wami owahletshunelwa lina\x + Seb. 20.7.\x*; lokhu kwenzeni ukungikhumbula\x + Heb. 10.3.\x*\x + Joha. 15.9.\x*\f + \fk ukungikhumbula: \fl Gr. \fq kube yisikhumbuzo sami.\f*.
\v 25 Ngokunjalo lenkezo, sebedlile\x + 11.21.\x*, yathi: Inkezo le iyisivumelwano esitsha egazini lami; lokhu kwenzeni, loba nini li\add yi\add*natha, ukungikhumbula.
