\v 27 Ngakho loba ngubani\x + Nani 9.10,13.\x* odla lesisinkwa kumbe anathe inkezo yeNkosi ngokungafanelanga\x + Joha. 13.27.\x*, uzakuba lecala\x + Mark. 3.29.\x* lomzimba legazi leNkosi\x + Joha. 6.51,53,56.\x*.
